<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/15790499-the-diary-of-a-single-parent-abroad"><img alt="The Diary of a Single Parent Abroad" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1386920594l/15790499._SX98_.jpg" />
